6a9a 17			            RLA  
6a9b 17			            RLA  
6a9c 17			            RLA  
6a9d cd a7 6a		            CALL Wr4bitsa       ;Write bits 0 to 3 of data byte  
6aa0 3e 96		            LD   A, 150  
